en:
{i}Emotional glee
Intoxicated, blissful
An old soul's rapture{/i}

{i}This sublime embrace
Deserved, garnered, the occult
Spellbound by your charm{/i}

{i}The wine flowing red
Purple will, blackened dresses
Dead eyes see white lies{/i}

{i}A girl of thirteen
Man, woman, infinity
Two must not be one{/i}

{i}Insecurity
Impatience and blasphemy
All lost to hatred{/i}
